body:
Oh, you can't have a space before the equals. It is looking for `"/home/zhao/Desktop/samples/=` because you have `logdir = X`, which it parses as `logdir='='`. 

Please use `logdir=X` or `logdir X`, the space is equivalent to an equals sign.
